# =============================================================================
# Copy to ".env.local" and fill in real values (never commit .env.local).
# =============================================================================

# --- Next.js site & Supabase (required for /registry, /intelligence, sitemap) ---
# Project Settings → API in Supabase dashboard
SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co
# "anon" "public" key — safe for browser/server reads where RLS allows (e.g. brand_intelligence SELECT)
SUPABASE_KEY=your_anon_public_key_here
# Optional: server-only; bypasses RLS — used for /go clicks etc. when configured in src/lib/supabase.ts
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key_here
#
# Footer + Quiz email capture write to public.lead_captures (anon INSERT/UPDATE on email).
# Quiz rows: source_path=/quiz, meta_data.source=quiz, meta_data.quiz_answers={...}

# Canonical site URL (sitemap, JSON-LD, metadata). Local dev example:
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000
# Optional: affiliate outbound base used by go-redirect helpers
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GO_REDIRECT_ORIGIN=https://your-production-domain.com

# --- Affiliate base URLs ---
# FluffCo (Impact) and Sleep & Beyond (CJ) have code defaults if unset.
# Saatva has NO default — without this, /go/{slug} sends direct merchant URLs (0 commission).
# CJ panel: copy the advertiser deep-link prefix ending in ?url= (or equivalent).
# AFFILIATE_IMPACT_FUFFCO=https://fluffco.pxf.io/c/6815113/3012270/26581?u=
# AFFILIATE_CJ_SLEEP_AND_BEYOND=https://www.tkqlhce.com/click-101698024-13814555?url=
# AFFILIATE_CJ_SAATVA=https://www.tkqlhce.com/click-YOUR_PID-YOUR_LINK_ID?url=
# Required for Saatva commission — without it, /go/{slug} is direct merchant (0%).

# --- UTM on /go/[slug] → final merchant URL (see src/lib/utm.ts) ---
# Default site preset is auto-appended. Per-channel examples:
#   /go/saatva-classic?utm_source=reddit&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=reddit_rss
#   /go/saatva-classic?utm_source=email&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=alert
#   /go/saatva-classic?utm_source=pinterest&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=pinterest
# productGoLink(slug, { channel: 'reddit', utm_content: 'hero_cta' }) in code.

# --- Compare / guides SEO (runtime reads audit_products) ---
# Auto pairs: same-brand + cross-brand within shelf (cap 72). Curated: src/data/compare-seo-pairs.json
# Regenerate snapshot: python src/scripts/generate_compare_pairs.py --write
# Guides RSS: https://your-domain.com/guides/rss.xml

# =============================================================================
# Intelligence center ("自建情报") — how data flows
# =============================================================================
# 1) READ on the site: pages use SUPABASE_URL + SUPABASE_KEY (anon) to SELECT
#    public.brand_intelligence (RLS policy allows read). Routes: /intelligence,
#    Cross_Platform_Signals on /registry/[slug].
# 2) WRITE your own rows: Supabase → Table Editor → brand_intelligence, or SQL,
#    or REST POST/PATCH with the service_role key (never expose in frontend).
#    Required alignment: brand_slug / product_slug must match audit_products.slug style.
# 3) Social evidence for audits: public.brand_social_corpus（Reddit 等，见第 5 条脚本）。
#    forensic_engine 只从该表组装舆情块，不再调用 Serper。
#    可选：审计单次从 corpus 拉取的最大行数
# BRAND_SOCIAL_CORPUS_AUDIT_MAX=400
#
# 4) Bulk brand_intelligence（corpus + DeepSeek，无 Serper）：
#    cd src/scripts && python brand_intel_bulk_ingest.py --limit 30
#    写入请用 service_role 的 SUPABASE_KEY。
#
# 5) Brand-level platform snippets → public.brand_social_corpus（默认仅 Reddit；全 registry：
#    cd src/scripts && python brand_social_corpus_ingest.py --from-registry
#    单品牌：python brand_social_corpus_ingest.py --brand Saatva
#    GitHub Actions：.github/workflows/brand-social-corpus-weekly.yml
#    每周六 21:00 UTC（周日北京时间 05:00）：① corpus ② brand_intelligence（需 DEEPSEEK_API_KEY）
#    先在 Supabase SQL Editor 执行：src/scripts/sql/brand_social_corpus.sql

# --- Python forensic pipeline (batch_scanner.py, forensic_engine.py) ---
# Same SUPABASE_URL / SUPABASE_KEY as above; for upserts that bypass RLS use service_role in SUPABASE_KEY locally or set service role in CI only.
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
# 法医审计 / brand_intel：优先 Gemini（JSON），失败或熔断后再 DeepSeek。二选一至少配 DEEPSEEK；配 Gemini 则先走 Gemini。
# GEMINI_API_KEY=   # 或 GOOGLE_API_KEY
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
# GEMINI_AUDIT_MAX_ATTEMPTS=3
# GEMINI_CIRCUIT_FAILURE_STREAK=5
# 两次 Gemini 请求之间的最小间隔（秒），减轻 RPM 限流；0=关闭。法医与 bulk ingest 同进程共用。
# GEMINI_MIN_INTERVAL_SEC=1.5
# Optional: batch_scanner.py sitemap origins (defaults are baked in for each brand)
# SB_SHOP_ORIGIN=https://sleepandbeyond.com
# FLUFFCO_SHOP_ORIGIN=https://home.fluff.co
# SAATVA_SITEMAP_URL=https://www.saatva.com/sitemap.xml
# TEMPURPEDIC_SHOP_ORIGIN=https://www.tempurpedic.com
# TEMPURPEDIC_SITEMAP_URL=https://www.tempurpedic.com/sitemap.xml
# BATCH_SCANNER_TARGETS_CACHE_HOURS=168
# BATCH_SCANNER_TARGETS_CACHE_PATH=

# --- Optional: scraping / Playwright / proxy (forensic_engine) ---
# PROXY_URL=http://127.0.0.1:7890
# PLAYWRIGHT_HEADED=0
# PLAYWRIGHT_SLOW_MO=0
# PLAYWRIGHT_CHROME_CHANNEL=
# PLAYWRIGHT_USER_AGENT=
# PLAYWRIGHT_FETCH_EXTRA_HEADERS=0
# COUPON_VALIDATE_HTTP=1

# --- Reddit RSS monitor (src/scripts/reddit_rss_monitor.py) — no Reddit API key ---
# Optional: same PROXY_URL as forensic_engine — RSS uses urllib; Gmail SMTP retries via PySocks tunnel if direct fails.
# If Reddit returns 403 Blocked, paste a desktop browser User-Agent from DevTools:
# REDDIT_RSS_USER_AGENT=Mozilla/5.0 ...
# If your port is SOCKS-only, use socks5://127.0.0.1:xxxx instead of http://...
# Use a Google "App Password" (2FA required): https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# GMAIL_USER=you@gmail.com
# GMAIL_PASS="your-app-password"   # quote required if value contains #
# Optional: override recipient (default: same as GMAIL_USER)
# GMAIL_TO=alerts@example.com
# Optional Gmail SMTP order (reddit_rss_monitor send_email):
# GMAIL_SMTP_TRY_DIRECT_FIRST=1
# GMAIL_SMTP_DIRECT_TIMEOUT_SEC=15
#
# Reply drafts: topic classification in reddit_reply_engine.py (not fixed brand scripts).
# REDDIT_ALERT_SKIP_IRRELEVANT=1 — default; no email when e.g. "hot sleeper" on a sheets-only thread.
# Preview: cd src/scripts && python reddit_rss_monitor.py --preview --title "..." --summary "..."
#
# GitHub Actions: .github/workflows/reddit-rss-monitor.yml (every 30 min UTC, --once)
# Secrets: GMAIL_USER, GMAIL_PASS, optional GMAIL_TO, REDDIT_RSS_USER_AGENT, PROXY_URL,
#          NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL

# --- Promo assets (src/scripts/promo_assets.py) ---
# GitHub Actions: .github/workflows/promo-assets-weekly.yml (Sun 20:00 UTC)
# Downloads: Actions artifact promo_output-* (Reddit drafts, Pinterest PNGs, JSON)
# Secrets: SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_KEY (service_role), NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL

# --- IndexNow (src/scripts/indexnow_ping.py) ---
# 1) Generate key: openssl rand -hex 16  → set INDEXNOW_KEY in .env and GitHub Secrets
# 2) Write verification file: cd src/scripts && python indexnow_ping.py --write-key-file
#    Commit public/{INDEXNOW_KEY}.txt and deploy (file body = key only).
# 3) GitHub Actions: .github/workflows/indexnow-ping.yml (daily 23:00 UTC + after batch scanner)
# Secrets: INDEXNOW_KEY, NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL, SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_KEY
